<div class="news-main" style="min-height:100px;">
  <h1 class="news-title">非洲男子发现706克拉巨钻 并决定捐给国家</h1>
  <div class="from fs12">
    <time id="news-time">2017-03-18 09:47:33</time>
    <span>[来源:中国新闻网]</span>
    <span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="news-content">
    <center>
	<a href="../../article/201703/201703171708066992.html#next" target="_self"><img src="http://i2.chinanews.com/simg/hd/2017/03/17/200x133_95a6fb5cb92d4eb1b4c04684a921ffae.jpg" border="0"></a> 
</center>
<p style="text-indent:2em;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;">
	非洲塞拉利昂一名男子近日发现了一枚重达706克拉的钻石，并决定上交给国家。
</p>
<center>
	<a href="../../article/201703/201703171708066992.html#next" target="_self"><img src="http://i2.chinanews.com/simg/hd/2017/03/17/200x133_3dae32418c8c4039b11c27a831a0a353.jpg" border="0"></a> 
</center>
<p style="text-indent:2em;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;">
	据外媒当地时间3月16日报道称，这枚钻石或将成为世界上第十三重的钻石，估计售价将达到4.25亿美元。
</p>
<center>
	<a href="../../article/201703/201703171708066992.html#next" target="_self"><img src="http://i2.chinanews.com/simg/hd/2017/03/17/200x133_a47e70b2e04d425da08c9ccbe77ad1ae.jpg" border="0"></a> 
</center>
<p style="text-indent:2em;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;">
	当地政府已经决定将这枚钻石进行公开拍卖，并将所得款项运用到国家和社区的建设上。
</p>
    
  </div>
</div>
